@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
title CI Release Flow

start
:Developer pushes tag;
:GitHub Actions triggered;
fork
  :Build Linux;
fork again
  :Build Windows;
fork again
  :Build macOS;
end fork
:Generate ZIP artifacts;
:Compute SHA256 checksums;
:Create GitHub Release;
:Attach artifacts to Release;
:Generate PR to Registry repo;
:Schema validation;
if (Valid?) then (yes)
  :Merge PR;
  :Registry updated;
else (no)
  :PR rejected;
endif
